                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890098",
        "quote": "We understand that we, as a brand, have transcended a brand, and we are part of our cultural identity, and there's a responsibility that comes with that.",
