    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890099",
        "quote": "I've always wanted Sundial Brands to be an inspiration to other minority-owned companies of how a business against all odds can achieve excellence, have significant social impact in our communities, and be successful on a world stage.",
