            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890100",
        "quote": "I am excited Sundial and Unilever have created this partnership, rooted in a purpose-driven ethos, that represents an incredible opportunity to take our Community Commerce economic empowerment and impact model to another level.",
