    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890089",
        "quote": "We started our company out of a need to survive, but we've built it based on a mission not only to help others survive but to prosper. Because of that, our purpose - to empower people to live more beautiful lives - compels us to keep community at our core.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richelieu Dennis",
            "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890089"
