    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890102",
        "quote": "As our company grew and we began growing our family stateside - with heritages ranging from Liberian and Sierra Leonean to Irish, Indian, Swedish, Filipino, German, and beyond - our different cultural influences and walks of life helped us even better understand the criticality of an inclusive point of view.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richelieu Dennis",
            "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890102"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Point Of View",
