                "name": "Grandmothers",
                "url": "/topics/grandmothers"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890075",
        "quote": "A critical lesson I learned is that we have to make sure all our employees, particularly new hires, have a full immersion in our culture.",
