    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890077",
        "quote": "As a kid growing up, one of the brands I thought was tremendous was Karl Kani... and I don't see Karl Kani today. I want to see SheaMoisture tomorrow.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richelieu Dennis",
            "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890077"
