                "name": "Brands",
                "url": "/topics/brands"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890078",
        "quote": "Once a company develops out of its consumer base, you will often see a well-funded multinational company come in and take over that space. The black-owned company either stays a niche company or just disappears. This is something we don't want to happen.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richelieu Dennis",
            "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890078"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Space",
                "url": "/topics/space"
