    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890084",
        "quote": "By questioning the very concept of a normal standard, especially as it applies to beauty and to hair type or texture, we can begin to see how arbitrary, narrow, and potentially destructive it is and course-correct ourselves on a path to where everybody gets love.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Richelieu Dennis",
            "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890084"
