    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/richelieu_dennis_890087",
        "quote": "My mother, Mary, has been a guiding force for as long as I can remember through the examples she's set as a single mother. She demonstrated her confidence and faith in me by investing everything in me and the business at a time when she had just lost everything.",
